Adult protocerebral MPP tachykinin neuro.SuperCategory: Adult tachykinin neuron of the central nervous system
Adult protocerebral MPP tachykinin neuro.Definition: Adult neuron that expresses tachykinin (FBgn0037976) and whose cell body is located in the median posterior protocerebrum. One cluster of around 3 cell bodies is found per hemisphere (Winther et al., 2003).
